Detection Challenges:
Rapid infrastructure rotation (IOC extinction)
Shared infrastructure across multiple threat actors
Traffic originates from legitimate residential IPs
Lack of static indicators
High false-positive risk if not baselined
Detection Strategy:
Focus shifts from indicators to behavior
Key Signals:
Abnormal VPN usage patterns
Geographic inconsistencies
Session anomalies
Unusual traffic from edge devices
Short-lived, high-churn connections
